IT GETS WORSE BEFORE IT GETS BETTER. ⁣
⁣
Contrary to popular belief, being a pro organizer is not a glamourous job. We work in and create (temporary) messes, sometimes injuring ourselves, all while working in close quarters and in every climate imaginable. But if you asked any one of us, we wouldn’t trade it for ANYTHING else! It takes a special kind of person to work in these conditions, and it’s important to see where all of these beautifully stunning spaces begin. ⁣
